title: BTS, Percent Departures On-Time at U.S. Airports, 1994
name: BTS, Percent Departures On-Time at U.S. Airports, 1994
description: This data reports the percent of flights that departed on time at U.S. airports in 1994.  The original data comes from monthly numbers “reported by U.S. certified air carrier that account for at least one percent of domestic scheduled passenger revenues – includes scheduled and actual arrival and departure times for flights.” www.bts.gov
